Variable k:ℕ
Variable n:ℕ

Metavariable R:Reference
Metavariable S(ℕ):Reference

Metavariable MetaInduction(ℕ):Reference

Metavariable P(ℕ):Statement

Metatheorem (MetaInduction(𝘻𝘦𝘳𝘰))
  P(𝘻𝘦𝘳𝘰)
  Proof
    P(𝘻𝘦𝘳𝘰) by R

Metatheorem (MetaInduction(𝘴𝘶𝘤𝘤𝘦𝘴𝘴𝘰𝘳(k)))
  P(𝘴𝘶𝘤𝘤𝘦𝘴𝘴𝘰𝘳(k))
  Proof
    P(k) by MetaInduction(k)
    P(k) ⇒ P(𝘴𝘶𝘤𝘤𝘦𝘴𝘴𝘰𝘳(k)) by S(k)
  Therefore
    P(𝘴𝘶𝘤𝘤𝘦𝘴𝘴𝘰𝘳(k)) by ModusPonens
